Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's stage is a white sandy beach!\NCouples come in varieties!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Scuba Diving Murder Case (Part 1)."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Saturday and Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You will?! Really?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! Just talking to a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This Saturday and Sunday!\NYou didn't have any plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really beautiful hotel and\Nits private beach is the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it costs the greatest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first break in a while,\Nso I'd rather drink and sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you drink and\Nsleep even when you are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I already promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no one! Nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come swimming\Ntoo, right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Don't teach him\Nto be lazy at such a young age!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the hotel's beach is\Nfilled with sexy women in swimsuits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's brimming with college\Ngirls and female office workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she saying? Ran is\Nusually against that kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have been working a lot lately.\NRecuperation might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! The old guy's the same\Nas ever, but what's up with Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The ocean's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sexy sea is calling for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:12.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Hotel, Izu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel definitely\Nlives up to its reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NAre you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Let's hurry and check in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've reserved two rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We don't need separate rooms.\NWouldn't a suite be cheaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd only get in the way later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing! Let's just change\Nand hurry to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Sexy girls are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too strange. Something is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah! Here it is, Dad!\NThe swimsuit I bought yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud! I don't want\Nanyone to know I have annoyances!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhh, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hey there, nice-bodied girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can rub that oil on you if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eri? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a wonderful coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're true lovebirds!\NIt's like you make a perfect pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you plotted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Plotted what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you got separate rooms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... it's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop being angry, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for secretly\Nbringing you together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy the Izu ocean more!\NOkay? Okay? Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until a hag showed up, wearing\Na swimsuit that didn't match her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and who was drooling\Nand howling at the sight of that hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Dad! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just embarrassed!\NHe hasn't seen you in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, he looks like a petty-minded\Nman who can't ever concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not wearing\Nyour wedding ring? You usually do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's on purpose.\NI was testing him to see if he'd notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there would\Nstill be hope if he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is a huge failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should quit with this\Nseparation and start my life over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wind up like that man, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I would ever want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could've happened?\NDad's been gone a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably back\Nat the beach, hitting on girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky to meet the great\NMori Kogoro-{\i1}san {\i0}in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor for me, too!\NTo think I have such charming female fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably just met them after\Nhe used the bathroom! And then--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his legs, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were clean before,\Nbut now there's sand up to his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily imagine him\Nkneeling in the sand to rub oil on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he brought\Nthem here to show off to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he actually--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should start\Na fan club or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran! These girls\Nsay they're fans of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with these two first!\NI met them on the beach just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Toda Kiwako, College Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Toda Kiwako-{\i1}san{\i0}, a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Matsuzaki Harumi-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuzaki Harumi, College Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How cute! Is this your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's Conan, an acquaintance's\Nkid who we're looking after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind him is my daughter, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the back is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his ex-wife, Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You're divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not necessarily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawazu Kunio, College Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy your age shouldn't be messin' with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Masahiko!\NYou say somethin', too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dear fiancée and sister\Nare bein' fooled, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You don't have to be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuzaki Masahiko, College Student
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he seems to be a celebrity,\Nso you can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Mori Kogoro-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthe famous "Sleeping Kogoro" detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I knew I recognized\Nyou from somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm that well-known?\NI'm at a loss for words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My face gets in papers and on\NTV all over, so I can't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you had lunch yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all have lunch together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a small restaurant\Nbehind this hotel. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're all part of\Nyour school's scuba diving club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we even had a dive\Nthis morning before lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your last time diving\Nsingle before the wedding next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll be diving tomorrow too,\Nso this isn't the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was tough getting my\Nbrother into this club! He can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to swim to dive.\NYou got an oxygen tank, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as a boy, Masahiko-{\i1}san\N{\i0}was never able to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Does that mean\Nyou two are childhood friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Childhood friends getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like my mom and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Right?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Childhood friends," huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many a couple have been\Nheartbroken by that sweet phrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing familiar friend and\Nfantasy is the height of foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think you'll need it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ever distrust your wife,\Njust call the Mori Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to receive major\Ncompensation from your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you divorce,\Njust call the Kisaki Law Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhere's your other childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiroshi said he was gonna\Ndo some snorkeling after the dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snore-killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diving without an air tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's diving without even eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is kind of strange;\Nhe likes the ocean more than women!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if he plans to marry a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Harumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask, but could you get\Na fresh beach towel from our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiwako.\NDon't tell me you're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I suddenly want\Nto take a dip in the ocean, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be alright drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do it today.\NCan't you go tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine! I haven't\Nhad that much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be some light snorkeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I join you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! I want to dive by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Harumi! Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean seems to be getting rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Kiwako is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi! You're with Kawazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran into each other in the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:09.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ito Hiroshi, College Student
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's diving spot was really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You didn't see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There she is! She's waving to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't seem right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Masahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Get back! You can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako! Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Masahiko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's here.\NHe came to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stud! You can carry her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Masahiko!\NShe probably just had a leg cramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me she--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. We told you not to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You can argue\Nall you want after you're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiwako. Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might've been bitten by a sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sea snake right by us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If so, then there should\Nbe fang marks somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hand... Left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Bite marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she was bitten by a sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we have to tie off the\Naffected area and suck out the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have anything\Nto use as a tourniquet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will a handkerchief do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know\Nit was a sea snake, little--?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the sea snake!\NIt was about forty centimeters long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought you\Nsaved her from drowning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake bit Kiwako-{\i1}san\N{\i0}on the back of her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Those are really poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he just run off with iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tannin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Washing the wound with the\Ntannin in tea to neutralize the poison
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the best emergency\Nmeasure for sea snake bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the person\Nwho sucks out the poison
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will need to wash\Ntheir mouth with tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how does that runt know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He's a pretty sharp boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's much more useful than we are,\Nas we twiddle our thumbs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though shouldn't you ask why\Na certain former police detective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't know about it instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll call the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ask the cook for\Nsome coarse tea full of tannin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwako... Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her fiancé. Can I come with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who saw the sea snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what type it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The type?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a picture book in the hotel office...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then contact the hospital as\Nsoon as you know what kind it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Office
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It was this sea snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black-banded sea krait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doing in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sometimes show up\Non the Kuroshio Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just a prickly feeling\Nand then no swelling after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so some fishermen have died\Nwithout ever noticing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let people swim in the ocean\Nwith such dangerous sea snakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishermen just happened to be bitten
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when sticking their hands in fish\Nnets that had also caught the snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we're talking\Nabout sea snakes here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely some might\Nsuddenly attack people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These snakes are docile and\Nnever attack people on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twenty-two years since\Nthis hotel was founded,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not a single visitor\Nhas been bitten by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, do any of these\Nsea snakes have wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings? No such variety exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall seeing small wings\Nbehind the head of the one I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed or something\Nmust've caught onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only my daughter could remember\Nso much from one quick look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only remember well\Nbecause it was so shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you have a wonderful\Npower of observation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a certain someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't even notice\Nhis wife's missing wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about your ring now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine she playfully\Nstuck her hand in the snake's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll go contact the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fang marks were no accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone held the snake and\Nforced it to bite her hand in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, was it one of\Nthe people who rushed to help her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everyone was empty-handed then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they rushed there because\NKiwako-{\i1}san {\i0}was drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one crazy enough\Nto have a sea snake ready
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they don't know if\Nsomeone will drown or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be more natural to think she\Nstarted to drown after she was bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means only\NHiroshi-{\i1}san {\i0}could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in the ocean\Njust before she drowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he could've had it bite her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his emergency treatment\Nafterward was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone go that far\Nto help someone they're trying to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, one of those four\Npeople was responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liked Kiwako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me?\NI can't find Kiwako's insurance card!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the towel at the bottom of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was no accident!\NAnd you're the one behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“The Scuba Diving Murder Case (Part 2).”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.11,0:24:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is part two.\N Who's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hotel employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:24:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
